    <p>LON­DON • Liver­pool have signed Greece de­fender Kostas Tsimikas from Olympiakos Pi­raeus on a long-term con­tract, the Pre­mier League cham­pi­ons an­nounced on Mon­day.</p>
    <p>While the fee was undis­closed, Bri­tish me­dia said it was £11 mil­lion (S$19.8 mil­lion), with the 24-year-old ear­marked as the un­der­study to first-choice left-back Andy Robert­son.</p>


